      "writtenOn": "2020-04-27T23:11:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It seemed better to just have a fixed flags part of the key for all geometric shapes, and then specialize their geometry writing. Most of the diff below is handling the new shape types that GrShape supports.",
